    "source": "FPbase: AausFP1",
    "sourceFigure": "FPbase",
    "note": "Excitation/emission are the FRET donor AausFP1 (AaFP1), the brightest known FP (Aequorea-derived; ex 504 / em 510, QY ~0.97). Jarvis = Acetabularia (Ace) rhodopsin acceptor + AaFP1 donor (confirmed: Quicke et al. 2026, Neuron; bioRxiv 2024.05.10.593541). The stored curve matches the FPbase AausFP1 spectrum (peaks 504/510); the Ace acceptor absorption (~525 nm) is not part of the displayed donor emission/excitation.",
